e scattered spectrum and halting\nthe instability. Our analyses are assisted and verified by numerous fluid and\nparticle-in-cell simulations. Based on our results, we discuss phenomena like\nthe pulse breakup and its different regimes, and assisted particle acceleration\nin presence of pulse evolutions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 25 Dec 2018 13:42:31 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 8 Jan 2019 08:33:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-06-11"}
