s. The non-phonon spin-fluctuation interaction in\nthe hole bands in the entire Co concentration range is small compared with the\nintraband electron-phonon interaction and is not dominant in the\n$Ba(Fe_{1-x}Co_{x})_{2}As_{2}$ family.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 25 Dec 2018 15:17:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-02-20"}
