ation axis, while the noise-level cold part of\nthe scatter tends to spread almost uniformly over a wide range of angles. The\nallowed energy diapasons within specific angular ranges are only partially\ncovered by the actual high-energy electron scatter.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 25 Dec 2018 02:00:19 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 10 Jan 2019 13:07:47 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 29 Jan 2019 22:07:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-11-19"}
